comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T18:26:37.352Z",codex-root,"Relationship rationale: the shell-composability story is not satisfied by one output flag. NDJSON streaming, stable script contracts, uniform envelopes, and indexed predicates form the minimum acceptance chain; each remains independently deliverable and backward-compatible."
